---
title: Easy Creamy Sausage Fusilli with Mushrooms and Peas
description: Fusilli is the perfect pasta for this creamy, meaty mushroom pasta. The peas add little pops of flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1006_W23_CA_RB154703-1_MAIN_low-1184447b.jpg
